            <title type="variant" xml:lang="ara-Latn-x-lc"/>
            <title type="translation" xml:lang="eng">Epistle in which is shown how the creature rediscovers the mnunity to which his essential being bears witness, and how he is brought into the presence of the human tree and the four spiritual birds.</title>
